                     <decoNote type="miniature">
                        <locus n="225v"/>
                        <persName key="person_101353608">Iskandar</persName> on the island near the "Lion's Mouth" whirlpool beating the wolfskin drum of the bronze talisman in order to still the waters. (One of the figures in the boat is shown in the likeness of <persName key="person_f5434">Ḥusain Bāiḳarā</persName>).</decoNote>
